         <abstract>
            <p>The text of the Life of St ʾEwosṭātewos, classified as 'redaction γ', characterised
               by devotion of <persName ref="PRS1854Amdase"/> to <persName ref="PRS3934Ewostate"/>,
               is believed to represent an elaborated shorter version of the 'redaction β', as
               noted in <bibl>
                  <ptr target="bm:Lusini1993Monachesimo"/>
                  <citedRange unit="page">43-45</citedRange>
               </bibl>. </p>
